  ('glute-bridge', 'Avoid prolonged supine positioning if uncomfortable or contraindicated; use elevated bridge, standing hip hinge activation, or wall-supported hip extension as alternatives.', 'No sex-based default. Scale by trunk control, hip control, coordination, sport demand, and symptoms.'),
